tHub, sync repos, setup workspace\n- **Development Workflow**: Planning → Implementation → Testing → Review\n- **Evening Routine**: Commit changes, update docs, backup\n- **Special Workflows**: bug_fix, hotfix, research\n\n### Script Files\n\n#### `scripts/agent-helper.sh` (Executable)\nMenu interaktif untuk:\n- Akses semua 7 agent\n- Workflow harian\n- Setup project baru\n- Cleanup workspace\n- Status check\n\n**Usage:**\n```bash\nbash .agent/scripts/agent-helper.sh\n```\n\n#### `scripts/quick-start.sh` (Executable)\nScript setup awal untuk:\n- Check prerequisites (Docker, Git, Node.js, Python)\n- Setup workspace structure\n- Create sample project\n\n**Usage:**\n```bash\nbash .agent/scripts/quick-start.sh\n```\n\n## Cara Penggunaan\n\n### 1. Mulai dengan Quick Start\n```bash\ncd /home/aseps/workspace\nbash .agent/scripts/quick-start.sh\n```\n\n### 2. Gunakan Helper Script\n```bash\nbash .agent/scripts/agent-helper.sh\n```\n\n### 3. Edit Konfigurasi\n```bash\n# Edit workspace config\ncode .agent/config/workspace.yaml\n\n# Edit orchestrator config\ncode .agent/config/orchestrator.yaml\n\n# Edit workflows\ncode .agent/workflows/daily-routine.yaml\n```\n\n### 4. Workflow Harian\n\n#### Pagi (08:00)\n1. Check notifikasi GitHub\n2. Sync repositories\n3. Setup workspace\n\n#### Siang (Development)\n1. Create feature branch\n2. Implementasi fitur\n3. Write tests\n4. Create PR\n\n#### Sore (17:00)\n1. Commit changes\n2. Update documentation\n3. Backup workspace\n\n## Custom	pending	\N	\N	2026-02-23 10:30:10.1546	\N
d9ed9146-291b-4e6d-bbf2-be793e0c8d5a	/home/aseps/workspace/agent/README.md	README.md	md	422d8ed0d7f7f20effbda833f031b5fd	umum	{"tags": ["dokumentasi", "konfigurasi"], "judul": "README.md", "status": "aktif", "doc_type": "dokumentasi", "instansi": null, "ringkasan": "Konfigurasi lengkap untuk memaksimalkan penggunaan agent dalam workspace sehari-hari.", "sub_domain": "umum", "tanggal_dokumen": null}	# 🤖 Agent Workspace Configuration\n\nKonfigurasi lengkap untuk memaksimalkan penggunaan agent dalam workspace sehari-hari.\n\n## 📁 Struktur Direktori\n\n```\n.agent/\n├── README.md              # Dokumentasi ini\n├── config/                # Konfigurasi agent\n│   ├── orchestrator.yaml  # Konfigurasi orchestrator\n│   └── workspace.yaml     # Konfigurasi workspace\n├── workflows/             # Workflow definitions\n│   └── daily-routine.yaml # Workflow harian\n├── scripts/               # Utility scripts\n│   └── agent-helper.sh    # Helper script interaktif\n└── templates/             # Template untuk berbagai keperluan\n```\n\n## 🚀 Cara Penggunaan\n\n### 1. Menggunakan Helper Script\n\n```bash\n# Jalankan helper script\nbash .agent/scripts/agent-helper.sh\n```\n\nScript ini menyediakan menu interaktif untuk:\n- 🤖 Mengakses semua agent (Orchestrator, Backend, Frontend, dll)\n- 📝 Menjalankan workflow harian\n- 🔧 Setup project baru\n- 🧹 Cleanup workspace\n\n### 2. Menggunakan Agent Langsung\n\n#### Orchestrator Agent\n```bash\n# Analyze task\ncurl -X POST orchestrator/analyze_task \\\n  -d '{"task_description": "your task"}'\n\n# Create fullstack app\ncurl -X POST orchestrator/create_fullstack_app \\\n  -d '{"app_name": "myapp", "project_path": "./projects"}'\n```\n\n#### Backend Agent\n```bash\n# Create Flask app\ncurl -X POST backend/create_flask_app \\\n  -d '{"name": "api", "directory": "./projects", "with_auth": true}'\n\n# Create API endpoint\ncurl -X POST backend/create_api_endpoint \\\n  -d '{"app_path": "./myapp", "resource_name": "users", "operations": ["create","read","update","delete"]}'\n```\n\n#### Frontend Agent\n```bash\n# Create React app\ncurl -X POST frontend/create_react_app \\\n  -d '{"name": "webapp", "directory": "./projects", "template": "typescript"}'\n\n# Create component\ncurl -X POST frontend/create_react_component \\\n  -d '{"name": "Button", "project_path": "./myapp", "with_styles": true}'\n```\n\n#### Testing Agent\n```bash\n# Setup unit testing\ncurl -X POST testing/setup_unit_testing \\\n  -d '{"project_path": "./myapp", "framework": "jest", "language": "typescript"}'\n\n# Run coverage\ncurl -X POST testing/run_test_coverage \\\n  -d '{"project_path": "./myapp", "test_type": "all"}'\n```\n\n## 📋 Workflow Harian\n\n### 🌅 Morning Routine (08:00)\n1. Check GitHub notifications\n2. List pending issues\n3. Sync repositories\n4. Setup workspace\n\n### 📝 Development Workflow\n1. **Planning**\n   - Create feature branch\n   - Analyze requirements\n\n2. **Implementation**\n   - Backend: Design & implement API\n   - Frontend: Design & implement UI\n   - Database: Setup migrations\n\n3. **Testing**\n   - Write unit tests\n   - Write integration tests\n   - Run test coverage\n\n4. **Review**\n   - Self code review\n   - Create pull request\n\n### 🌆 Evening Routine (17:00)\n1. Commit all changes\n2. Update documentation\n3. Log daily progress\n4. Backup workspace\n\n## 🔧 Konfigurasi\n\n### Workspace Preferences\nEdit `.agent/config/workspace.yaml` untuk mengubah:\n- Default language (id/en)\n- Timezone (Asia/Jakarta)\n- Development preferences\n- Projec	pending	\N	\N	2026-02-23 10:30:10.1546	\N
