1b195157-0548-4948-8c59-fd84603d2f1e	/home/aseps/workspace/POSTGRESQL_FIX_MANUAL.md	POSTGRESQL_FIX_MANUAL.md	md	0be40d5413529ad7597b1409bedbd6b0	umum	{"tags": ["postgresql", "fix", "manual"], "judul": "POSTGRESQL_FIX_MANUAL", "status": "aktif", "doc_type": "manual", "instansi": "null", "ringkasan": "Mengatasi masalah autentikasi password PostgreSQL tanpa password", "sub_domain": "umum", "tanggal_dokumen": "2024-04-15"}	# 🔧 PostgreSQL Fix Manual\n\n## Masalah\nPostgreSQL memerlukan autentikasi password yang tidak diketahui.\n\n## Solusi: Ubah ke Trust Mode (Tanpa Password)\n\n### ⚠️ PENTING: Urutan Langkah\n**HARUS ubah pg_hba.conf dulu, baru bisa login tanpa password!**\n\n---\n\n### Step 1: Edit pg_hba.conf\n```bash\nsudo nano /etc/postgresql/16/main/pg_hba.conf\n```\n\n### Step 2: Ubah baris berikut:\n\n**Cari bagian IPv4 local connections:**\n```\n# IPv4 local connections:\nhost    all             all             127.0.0.1/32            scram-sha-256\n```\n\n**Ubah menjadi:**\n```\n# IPv4 local connections:\nhost    all             all             127.0.0.1/32            trust\n```\n\n**Cari bagian IPv6 local connections:**\n```\n# IPv6 local connections:\nhost    all             all             ::1/128                 scram-sha-256\n```\n\n**Ubah menjadi:**\n```\n# IPv6 local connections:\nhost    all             all             ::1/128                 trust\n```\n\n**Cari bagian Local socket:**\n```\nlocal   all             postgres                                peer\nlocal   all             all                                     peer\n```\n\n**Ubah menjadi:**\n```\nlocal   all             postgres                                trust\nlocal   all             all                                     trust\n```\n\n### Step 3: Restart PostgreSQL\n```bash\nsudo systemctl restart postgresql\n```\n\n---\n\n### Step 4: Create User dan Database (TANPA PASSWORD!)\n```bash\npsql -h localhost -U postgres -d postgres\n```\n\n**Tidak perlu password sekarang!** Langsung tekan Enter jika diminta password.\n\nKemudian jalankan SQL:\n```sql\n-- Create user\nCREATE USER rag_user WITH PASSWORD 'rag_password_2024';\nALTER USER rag_user WITH SUPERUSER;\n\n-- Create database\nCREATE DATABASE rag_knowledge;\nGRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE rag_knowledge TO rag_user;\n\n-- Exit\n\\q\n```\n\n### Step 5: Test Koneksi\n```bash\nPGPASSWORD=rag_password_2024 psql -h localhost -U rag_user -d rag_knowledge -c "SELECT current_user;"\n```\n\n### Step 6: Jalankan Backup\n```bash\ncd /home/aseps/workspace && python3 backup_to_supabase_storage.py\n```\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Catatan Keamanan\nTrust mode memudahkan development tapi kurang aman untuk production. Untuk production, kembalikan ke `scram-sha-256` setelah setup selesai.\n	pending	\N	\N	2026-03-10 08:00:01.472565	\N
